name: Tree 0009 : The Pomme-Pomme Girl
description:
They are everywhere : family tree, in computer science, in nature or in painting! I love trees and I started to plant a forest and now you can adopt it! 
Why Pomme pomme Girl? Because in French a Pom-Pom Girl is a cheerleader.. And a pomme is an apple.. So this tree is an apple tree? No but I like the word Pom-Pom girl!
